Name: Bundle Kitt
About the game: Play as Bundle Kitt (a baby cat who is always cold and wears a blanket) in this short 5 minute sidescrolling adventure. A series of micro scenes, what trouble will Bundle Kitt get into today? WASD, or arrow keys, and Space Bar to play.
